                            </div>
                            <h4>Branding</h4>
                        </div>
                        <div class="service-text">
                            <p>We have a lot of laptops with strong brands such as Dell, Apple, Huawei and etc.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div> <!-- /.col -->
                <!-- Service Item 2 -->
                <div class="col-md-4 m-bottom-20">
                    <div class="service service-type-2 wow fadeIn" data-wow-duration="1s" data-wow-delay="0.8s">
                        <div class="service-header clearfix">
                            <div class="service-icon pull-left">
                                <i class="fa fa-rocket" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                            </div>
                            <h4>Fast Delivery</h4>
                        </div>
                        <div class="service-text">
                            <p>Our products reach you as soon as possible within two days inside the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia and less than a week outside it.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div> <!-- /.col -->
                <!-- Service Item 3 -->
                <div class="col-md-4 m-bottom-20">
                    <div class="service service-type-2 wow fadeIn" data-wow-duration="1s" data-wow-delay="1s">
                        <div class="service-header clearfix">
                            <div class="service-icon pull-left">
                                <i class="fa fa-comments-o" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                            </div>
                            <h4>24/7 Support</h4>
                        </div>
                        <div class="service-text">
                            <p>You can contact us at any time you want. Do not be hesitate always at your service.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div> <!-- /.col -->

            </div> <!-- /.row -->
        </div> <!-- /.container -->
    </section>
    <!-- End Services -->
    <!-- Start About -->
    <section id="about" class="light-bg p-top-80 p-bottom-40">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-7 col-md-8 col-sm-12 m-bottom-30 wow zoomIn" data-wow-duration="1s" data-wow-delay="0.6s">
                    <video class="vid-responsive" controls autoplay="autoplay" loop>
                        <source src="~/assets/img/about_vid.mp4" type=video/mp4>
                    </video>
                </div> <!-- /.col -->
                <div class="col-lg-5 col-md-4 col-sm-12">
                    <!-- Section Title -->
                    <div class="m-bottom-30">
                        <h2 class="wow fadeIn" data-wow-duration="1s" data-wow-delay="0.6s">About Us</h2>
                        <div class="divider-small wow zoomIn" data-wow-duration="1s" data-wow-delay="0.7s"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="wow zoomIn" data-wow-duration="1s" data-wow-delay="0.6s">
                        <p>At Aroma, you find all the premium laptops you need and you can buy them in a smooth and safe way without any hassles with a two-year warranty.</p>
                        <p>In addition, all that you see is hand-picked and 100% true – sourced straight from the best brands and their approved affiliates from the US and over the world, only for you.</p>
                    </div>
                    <a data-scroll href="~/#contact" class="m-top-30 btn btn-main btn-theme wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.7s">Contact Us</a>
                </div> <!-- /.col -->

            </div> <!-- /.row -->
        </div> <!-- /.container -->
    </section>
    <!-- End About -->
    <!-- Start New Sale -->
    <section id="newSale" class=" p-top-80 p-bottom-80">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <!-- Section Title -->
                <div class="section-title text-center m-bottom-30">
                    <h2 class="wow fadeInDown" data-wow-duration="1s" data-wow-delay="0.6s">Newest Sales</h2>
                    <div class="divider-center-small wow zoomIn" data-wow-duration="1s" data-wow-delay="0.6s"></div>
                    <p class="section-subtitle wow fadeInUp" data-wow-duration="1s" data-wow-delay="0.6s"><em class="">Check our newest product.</em></p>
                </div>
                <!-- === newest sale Form === -->
                <div class="col-lg-7 col-md-12 col-sm-12 p-bottom-30">
                    <div class="newest-form row">
                        <div class="col-sm-12 contact-form-item wow zoomIn">
                            <img src="~/assets/img/laptops/Surface_Laptop Go_01.jpg" alt="newest-sale" class="img-responsive wow fadeInLeft" style="" data-wow-duration="1s" data-wow-delay="0.6s" />
                        </div>
                    </div> <!-- /.newest sale-form & inner row -->
                </div> <!-- /.col -->
                <!-- === newest sale Information === -->
                <div class="col-lg-5 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
                    <div class="newest-info">
                        <!-- === Details === -->
                        <div class="m-top-20 wow zoomIn">
                            <div class="newest-info-title"> Microsoft | Surface Go </div>
                            <div class="sub-info-title"> Every Day, Everywhere </div>
                            <div class="newest-info-text">
                                Get the most out of every day by getting the authored look
                            </div>
                            <div class="sub-info-title"> Stylish Design and Great Value </div>
                            <div class="newest-info-text">
                                See and do more on the 12.45" touchscreen, unique premium materials and a selection of colours, all at an exceptional value.
                            </div>
                            <div class="sub-info-title"> The Lightest Surface Laptop </div>
                            <div class="newest-info-text">
                                Get all your style, advanced performance and all-day battery life, at an exceptional value.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div> <!-- /.col -->
                <!-- === newest sale Form === -->
                <div class="col-lg-7 col-md-12 col-sm-12 p-top-30" style="float:right">
                    <div class="newest-form row">
                        <div class="col-sm-12 contact-form-item wow zoomIn">
                            <img src="~/assets/img/laptops/Surface_Laptop-Go_02.jpeg" alt="newest-sale" class="img-responsive wow fadeInLeft" style="" data-wow-duration="1s" data-wow-delay="0.6s" />
                        </div>
                    </div> <!-- /.newest sale-form & inner row -->
                </div> <!-- /.col -->
                <!-- === newest sale Information === -->
                <div class="col-lg-5 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
                    <div class="newest-info">
                        <!-- === Details === -->
                        <div class="m-top-20 wow zoomIn">
                            <div class="newest-price"> SAR 2,649.00 </div>
                            <div class="newest-info-text">
                                Pay 127 SAR for 36 months !
                            </div>
                            <a href="#" class="btn btn-main btn-theme wow fadeInUp btn-newest" data-wow-delay="0.8s">Order Now</a>

                        </div>

                    </div>
                </div> <!-- /.col -->               
            </div> <!-- /.row -->
        </div> <!-- /.container -->
    </section>
    <!-- End  New Sale -->
    <!-- Start Stat -->
    <section id="stat" class="parallax-bg overlay-dark p-top-80 p-bottom-40 white-color" style="background-image:url(../assets/img/bg2.jpg)" data-stellar-background-ratio="0.5">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">

                <!-- === Stats Item 1 === -->
                <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 p-bottom-40">
                    <div class="stat-item stat-item-type-2 wow zoomIn" data-wow-duration="1s" data-wow-delay="0.3s">
                        <div class="stat-item-icon">
                            <i class="fa fa-laptop"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-item-number">
                            120
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-item-text">
                            Laptops Sold
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div> <!-- /.col -->
                <!-- === Stats Item 2 === -->
                <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 p-bottom-40">
                    <div class="stat-item stat-item-type-2 wow zoomIn" data-wow-duration="1s" data-wow-delay="0.4s">
                        <div class="stat-item-icon">
                            <i class="fa fa-users"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-item-number">
                            102
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-item-text">
                            Happy Customers
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div> <!-- /.col -->
                <!-- === Stats Item 3 === -->
                <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 p-bottom-40">
                    <div class="stat-item stat-item-type-2 wow zoomIn" data-wow-duration="1s" data-wow-delay="0.6s">
                        <div class="stat-item-icon">
                            <i class="fa fa-trophy"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-item-number">
                            55
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-item-text">
                            Awards Received
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div> <!-- /.col -->

            </div> <!-- /.row -->
        </div> <!-- /.container -->
    </section>
    <!-- End Stat -->
    <!-- Start Contact -->
    <section id="contact" class="dark-bg p-top-80 p-bottom-80">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <!-- Section Title -->
                <div class="section-title text-center m-bottom-30">
                    <h2 class="white-color wow fadeInDown" data-wow-duration="1s" data-wow-delay="0.6s">Contact</h2>
                    <div class="divider-center-small divider-white wow zoomIn" data-wow-duration="1s" data-wow-delay="0.6s"></div>
                    <p class="section-subtitle wow fadeInUp" data-wow-duration="1s" data-wow-delay="0.6s"><em>You can contact us at any time you want.<br>Do not be hesitate always at your service.</em></p>
                </div>
                <!-- === Contact Form === -->
                <div class="col-md-7 col-sm-7 p-bottom-30">
                    <div class="contact-form row">

                        <form name="ajax-form" id="ajax-form" action="contact.php" method="post">
                            <div class="col-sm-6 contact-form-item wow zoomIn">
                                <input name="name" id="name" type="text" placeholder="Your Name: *" />
                                <span class="error" id="err-name">please enter name</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-sm-6 contact-form-item wow zoomIn">
                                <input name="email" id="email" type="text" placeholder="E-Mail: *" />
                                <span class="error" id="err-email">please enter e-mail</span>
                                <span class="error" id="err-emailvld">e-mail is not a valid format</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-sm-12 contact-form-item wow zoomIn">
                                <textarea name="message" id="message" placeholder="Your Message"></textarea>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-sm-12 contact-form-item">
                                <button class="send_message btn btn-main btn-theme wow fadeInUp" id="send" data-lang="en">submit</button>
                            </div>
                            <div class="clear"></div>
                            <div class="error text-align-center" id="err-form">There was a problem validating the form please check!</div>
                            <div class="error text-align-center" id="err-timedout">The connection to the server timed out!</div>
                            <div class="error" id="err-state"></div>
                        </form>

                        <div class="clearfix"></div>
                        <div id="ajaxsuccess">Successfully sent!!</div>
                        <div class="clear"></div>

                    </div> <!-- /.contacts-form & inner row -->
                </div> <!-- /.col -->
                <!-- === Contact Information === -->
                <div class="col-md-5 col-sm-5">
                    <address class="contact-info">


                        <!-- === Location === -->
                        <div class="m-top-20 wow slideInRight">
                            <div class="contact-info-icon">
                                <i class="fa fa-location-arrow"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="contact-info-title">
                                Address:
                            </div>
                            <div class="contact-info-text">
                                King Fahd Rd, Al Salmaniyah, Al Hofuf
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- === Phone === -->
                        <div class="m-top-20 wow slideInRight">
                            <div class="contact-info-icon">
                                <i class="fa fa-phone"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="contact-info-title">
                                Phone number:
                            </div>
                            <div class="contact-info-text">
                                (+966) 100200311
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- === Mail === -->
                        <div class="m-top-20 wow slideInRight">
                            <div class="contact-info-icon">
                                <i class="fa fa-envelope"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="contact-info-title">
                                Email:
                            </div>
                            <div class="contact-info-text">
                                support247@support.com
                            </div>
                        </div>

                    </address>
                </div> <!-- /.col -->

            </div> <!-- /.row -->
        </div> <!-- /.container -->
    </section>
    <!-- End Contact -->
</body>
</html>